description:
[h1][b]The Modpack WEAPONS[/b][/h1]
This is the Modpack WEAPONS and contains EXPLOSIVE and EXPERIMENTAL weapons. Flamethrower! Grenadelauncher! And more!
Explode stuff and play warfare with the latest in weapon technology!

Parts from this mod currently include weapons you might find in The Modpack and The Modpack Beta, but more is planned soon!

- Weekly updates!
- Improved algorithms! Fire and other libraries!
- Super Experimental weapons! Force field! Carpet Bomber! PaintBomb! And More!(Don't be afraid to suggest ANYTHING!)

Created by:
[b][url=https://www.youtube.com/c/brentbatch]Brent Batch[/url], Durf, MJM, TechnologicNick, Lord Pain[/b], Grego, Shinevision

Like the mods?
[img]https://i.imgur.com/p7Fv1Z6.gif[/img]
Don't forget to leave a thumbs up!
